I made one narrow Stage-2 transfer improvement: when `init_from_model_path` has a different `max_seq_length`, `position_embedding.weight` is now partially copied by overlapping rows instead of being skipped.
This preserves tokenizer/embedding/output-head stability while improving initialization quality for the next full-response train.
